View_Interfaces

Interface ICustomerTab

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ITab, IView, java.util.Observer
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CustomerTab

    public interface ICustomerTab
extends ITab
    This tab interface provides functionality to edit the saved information about the customer. The tab has multiple text fields in which the user can enter information about the customer of this project. In addition this view has two view actions which the user can take:
    • ViewActions.SAVE - saves the new information in the requirement analysis
    • ViewActions.EDIT_CE - resets all text fields to the saved information (use resetData()
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    9045534
    See Also:
